																																												</figure>
																																											</div>
																																											<div class="emm-container__grid">
																																												<h2>4. Create a restful environment</h2>
																																												<p>Simple things can have a big impact when it comes to falling asleep and staying asleep.</p>
																																												<p>It&#x27;s generally easier to drop off when it&#x27;s cool, dark and quiet – but the right sleep environment is personal, so try different things and see what works for you.</p>
																																												<p>Wearing earplugs, putting your phone on silent and face down (or out of the room entirely), keeping clocks out of view and making sure the room is well ventilated can all make a big difference.</p>
																																												<p>Some people also find playing ambient sounds like rainfall, gentle music or white noise helpful.</p>
																																											</div>
																																										</div>
																																									</div>
																																								</div>
																																							</div>
																																						</section>
